schools.name: Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. Early College

data.description:
Introducing a two-story, 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home in the sought-after area of Green Valley Ranch. As you enter, be greeted by the warmth of a fireplace and the grandeur of vaulted ceilings, creating an inviting ambiance in the living space. Gleaming hardwood floors lead you through the home, adding warmth and elegance to the space.

The primary bedroom offers a serene retreat with its luxurious 5-piece ensuite bath, providing a spa-like experience. Step outside onto the deck, added in 2023, where you can bask in the tranquility of the surroundings, unwinding amidst nature or entertain guests in style.

The kitchen is a culinary delight, featuring granite countertops and modern appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. Additionally, this home boasts a finished basement with a bedroom, bath, great room, an office space, perfect for remote work or quiet productivity and a craft room for all your creativity.

With its blend of timeless features and contemporary amenities, this home is a true sanctuary for modern living. Conveniently located near the Gaylord of the Rockies, DIA, grocery stores, Costco, restaurants, Green Valley Ranch 18-Hole Championship Golf Course and so much more.  Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours! 

 This home also has a newly installed solar system. Buyer will need to qualify for solar lease.
